<headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 03 at 6:39AM MST  by NWS Goodland</headline>
<description>Areas of fog and freezing fog with visibilities less than 1 mile
at times, isolated areas of one quarter mile visibility are
possible. The freezing fog may create some slick spots on elevated
surfaces such as bridges and overpasses. Be prepared for rapid
reductions in visibility if driving this morning. The fog is
expected to diminish during the mid to late morning hours.</description>
